						               													<description>Action Dice Games! Super Fun Game - Portable, Playing Dice : Perfect For Tailgating at Games, Travel, Home, Parties, Gifts, Stocking Suffers and anywhere you want to play a full sports game fast and realistic.  You call the plays and decide when to go for the bomb or long shot!  Solo or versus, these games are action packed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game can be single or two players.  To play the game simply choose one of the five offensive plays and roll the dice to see the result.  Each team gets a chance to move the ball down field to score points by calling their own plays.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Keeping track of time in this football game is easy. Provided are score sheets. Each time a play is finished the user will record the down and yardage on this score sheet. After 30 plays are completed, it will show the final score for that quarter of play. The team with the most points wins the game. If the score is tied then an overtime quarter will begin.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;What makes Action Dice Games unique is the fact that they are pocket sized, accurate to the professional leagues and very fast results.  There is no play art, player strengths or formations. The result is based off the play you call and the situation you call the play during these games will determine the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
